hits.definition:
害

[hài] harmful;

    害虫 hàichóng destructive insect;

    厉害 lìhai fierce

杨 (F 楊)

[yáng] poplar tree;

    三角叶杨 sānjiǎoyèyáng cottonwood

料

[liào] (= 材料 cáiliào) material, expect, anticipate;

    资料 zīliào means, data, material

州

[zhōu] prefecture;

    广州 Guǎngzhōu Canton

急

[jí] urgent;

    着急 zháojí anxious;

    急忙 jímáng in a hurry

低

[dī] low;

    降低 jiàngdī reduce;

    低级 dījí elementary;

    高低 gāodī height

岁 (F 歲)

[suì] years old;

    岁数 suìshu age;

    万岁 wànsuì long life, Your/His Majesty, "Banzai"

酒

[jiǔ] wine;

    啤酒 píjiǔ beer;

    喝酒 hējiǔ drink wine

河

[hé] river;

    河南省 Hénán shěng Henan Province;

    运河 yùnhé canal

初

[chū] beginning, first (in order);

    初步 chūbù preliminary;

    起初 qǐchū at first
